            </rs>. Aged 25. - <rs id="t18291203-105-punish556" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18291203-105-punish556" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291203-105-defend734 t18291203-105-punish556"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
